To get the "Rainbow" effect, all one has to do is wet sand the Bus down,
lay a coat of clear with pearl in it, and the pearl comes in many
hue's-----green, blue, red, purple, etc. and then lay a coat of clear on
top of that-----time consuming but neat-----

Terry


 
